Safari Industries India Ltdhas informed BSE that the meeting of the Board of Directors of the Company is scheduled on 10/11/2025 inter alia to consider and approve amongst other matters:

1. the Unaudited Standalone and Consolidated Financial Results of the Company for the quarter and half year ended 30th September 2025;
2. Declaration of Interim Dividend on equity shares for financial year 2025-26 if any.
